        <img src="/images/Learning.gif" alt="Tutoring session">
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
<section class="about" id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Elevated Tutors are not just tutors, they’re the big sibling that students didn’t know they needed. Their mission is to help students and young adults reach academic goals while guiding them toward a greater sense of self and purpose. Whether it’s acing the next exam, exploring future careers, or defining what success looks like on a personal level, Elevated tutors are there every step of the way. Combining tutoring with mentorship and coaching, they use modern tools and a personalized approach to support each student’s unique journey. More than just grades, their focus is on growth in the areas of academics, personal, and beyond. With a blend of intelligence, heart, and strategy, they help build futures as ambitious as the students they serve.
    </p>
    <div class="about">

        <img src="/images/Learning.gif" alt="About Elevated Tutors">
    </div>
</section>

